     wrap--Markdown-table-01.test, wrap--Markdown-table-02.test,
     wrap--Markdown-table-03.test, wrap--Markdown-table-04.test,
     wrap--Markdown-table-05.test, wrap--Markdown-table-06.test,
     wrapc--Markdown-table-01.test, wrapc--Markdown-table-02.test,
     wrapc--Markdown-table-03.test, wrapc--Markdown-table-04.test,
     wrapc--Markdown-table-05.test, wrapc--Markdown-table-06.test: Added PHP
     Markdown Extra table support.
   * markdown.c: s/nested_list_indent/nested_indent_min/
   * markdown.c: Fixed comment.
   * wrap.1: More explicit about what Markdown is and is not currently
     supported.

