   * wrapc.1: 1. Added Fortran. 2. Indented comment delimiters.
   * test/Makefile.am, wrapc-D-01.txt, wrapc-D_style-01.txt, wrapc-D-01.txt,
     wrapc-D_style-01.txt, wrapc-D-01.test, wrapc-D_style-01.test: Change -D
     test; added D test.
   * wrapc.1, wrapc.c: Replaced delim(eter) with char(acter) in some places.
   * wrapc.c: Even better handling of two-character delimiters.
   * wrapc.1: Updated comments/languages.
   * wrapc.c: Added comment.
   * wrapc.c: A static buf is null by default.
   * wrapc.c: Better implementation/comments for multi-character delimiters.
   * wraprc.5: 1. Added mention of what happens of a file matches more than one
     pattern. 2. Added 'c' example alias.

